      "explanation": "First T flip-flop at x=0-3. Button input at (0,1,1). RS latch core: NOR torches at (2,0,0) and (2,0,2), cross-coupled by dust at x=3 z=0→1→2. Lamp at (3,0,-1) shows bit 0. Each button press toggles this bit.",
